entries.journal_entry_description: Frelka ran into someone--or something!--named the Rak'qua Aphotic. His droid, E-5KL, wants you to help him avenge Frelka's pride. Hunt down the Rak'qua Aphotic and save the day!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find the Rak'qua Aphotic and defeat him. E-5KL said he was in the beginning of this horrible place! He shouldn't be hard to miss.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: The Hunt: Defeat the Rak'qua Aphotic
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to E-5KL in Station Gamma at the entrance.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have avenged Frelka, now it is time to leave Gamma to tell him about it.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Frelka on Tansarii Point Station and give him the good news.
